productReviews.reviewText: My co-worker Reed has one of these. He says it looks microscopic.
My co-worker Bryton has one of these. He says it looks ragged.
This open-source works outstandingly well. It grudgingly improves my baseball by a lot.
The box this comes in is 5 yard by 6 centimeter and weights 18 gram!!
I saw one of these in Moldova and I bought one.
